{
  "texts": [
    "Effects MeasuresWe opted for the French versions of the following self-reported measures based on the recommendations of the Initiative on Methods, Measurement, and Pain Assessment in Clinical Trials [39] (Table 2).",
    "Statistical AnalysesWe performed descriptive statistics using means (SD) for continuous outcomes and frequencies (%) for categorical outcomes.",
    "We compared pre-, post-, and follow-up intervention scores for effect measures using repeated-measures linear models.",
    "All statistical analyses were conducted using R software (version 4.3.0; R Foundation for Statistical Computing) in RStudio (version 2023.06.0; Posit PBC) [46,47].",
    "Models were fit using lme4 (version 1.1-33; R Foundation for Statistical Computing) [48]."
  ]
}